:"2020-04-21T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"其中一段preview<br />\n心智圖<br />\n說明<br />\n說明心智圖，又稱腦圖、心智地圖、腦力激盪圖、思維導圖、靈感觸發圖、概念地圖、或思維地圖，是一種圖像式思維的工具以及一種利用圖像式思考輔助工具來表達思維的工具。 心智圖是使用一個中央關鍵詞或想法引起形象化的構造和分類的想法;它用一個中央關鍵詞或想法以輻射線形連接所有的代表字詞、想法、任務或其它關聯專案的圖解方式。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BF%83%E6%99%BA%E5%9B%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%259B%25BE&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiYT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=5abdd87e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BF%83%E6%99%BA%E5%9B%BE</a>"},{"pid":"375a2dbfb29f3925893512b85a44564265eb3d0e","tid":1982211,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b937a22052d06b55db1393889dc0f8de0183af","tid":1982211,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5758362cf2d71f78f18374c452df332c86379053","tid":1982211,"uid":76115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"如果我輯埋成本Notebooks for an Interpretation of Sigma's Thought<br />\n有幾多人會買"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPZFxno.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPZFxno.jpg&h=929b9a97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊本深d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"我嗰本啦<br />\n工聯會廢佬識乜哲學"},{"pid":"c0582cf7f1572b898f2e2cd582b9afa0353ec0d9","tid":1982211,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"375a2dbfb29f3925893512b85a44564265eb3d0e","tid":1982211,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b937a22052d06b55db1393889dc0f8de0183af","tid":1982211,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5758362cf2d71f78f18374c452df332c86379053","tid":1982211,"uid":76115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"如果我輯埋成本Notebooks for an Interpretation of Sigma's Thought<br />\n有幾多人會買"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:18:25.00